    dc:date "2009" ;
    dc:title "A new tree-frog genus and species from Ivory Coast, West Africa (Amphibia: Anura: Hyperoliidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186395>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186396>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186397>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186398>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186399>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186400>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186401>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186402> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186395>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Variation in gular gland size of adult male Morerella cyanophthalma sp. nov. Top left: MHNG 2131.43, SVL: 29.0 mm; top right: MHNG 2131.44 (holotype), SVL: 30.1 mm; bottom left: MHNG 2131.41, SVL: 24.8 mm; bottom right MHNG 2131.51, SVL: 27.1 mm; scale bar = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186395/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186396>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Right hand (a, b), finger-tip (c), foot (e) and toe-tip (f) and left hand (d) and foot (g) of adult male Morerella cyanophthalma sp. nov. (a, b, c, e, f: scans of MHNG 2131.36, paratype; d, g: drawings of MHNG 2131.44, holotype); scale bar = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186396/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186397>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Life adult female (above) and males (below) Morerella cyanophthalma sp. nov. from Banco National Park, Ivory Coast (top and bottom right: photo by Dieter Mahsberg)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186397/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186398>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Volume rendering of X-ray microtomography of a male Morerella cyanophthalma sp. nov. skull (MNHG 3121 - 36) in dorsal (a), ventral (b), lateral (c), anterior (d) and posterior view (e)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186398/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186399>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Hyoid apparati of adult male Morerella cyanophthalma sp. nov.; drawing after clearing and staining (a: drawing from ZMB 71566, scale bar = 1 mm; b: scan of MHNG 3121 - 36)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186399/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186400>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Pectoral girdle and vertebral column of adult male Morerella cyanophthalma sp. nov. Pectoral apparati of SMNS 11940 (a: drawing after clearing and staining) and MNHG 3121 - 36 (b: scan). Vertebral column (scan of MHNG 3121 - 36) in dorsal (c) and ventral (d) view. CL = clavicle, CO = coracoid, ECO = epicoracoid, OM = omnosternum, ST = sternum; scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186400/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186401>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Sonogram and waveform of advertisement calls of Morerella cyanophthalma sp. nov. White noise in basic frequencies is due to the noise of the climate chamber where the frogs were kept." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186401/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186402>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Morerella cyanophthalma sp. nov. tadpoles; a: lateral view of a Gosner stage 37 tadpole (ZMB 71591); b: mouth of tadpole (Gosner stage 37) showing labial tooth rows and papillae (left; scale bar = 200 μm) and c: keratodonts (right; scale bar = 10 μm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186402/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

